detaileddescription.para: Constructor for a CranesSystem. The queueing discipline and the capacity limit of the underlying queues for the cranes and for the transporters can be chosen.

parameterdescription.para: Model : The model this CranesSystem is associated to.
int : determines the sort order of the underlying cranes queue implementation. Choose a constant from QueueBased like QueueBased.FIFO or QueueBased.LIFO or ...
int : The capacity of the cranes queue, that is how many cranes can be enqueued. Zero (0) means unlimited capacity.
int : determines the sort order of the underlying transporter queue implementation. Choose a constant from QueueBased like QueueBased.FIFO or QueueBased.LIFO or ...
int : The capacity of the transporter queue, that is how many transporters can be enqueued. Zero (0) means unlimited capacity.
boolean : Flag, if this CranesSystem should produce a report or not.
boolean : Flag for trace to produce trace messages.
